                Native iOS Development
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-primary-400 rounded-full mt-2 mr-3 flex-shrink-0"></span>
                Native Android Development
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-primary-400 rounded-full mt-2 mr-3 flex-shrink-0"></span>
                Cross-platform Development
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-primary-400 rounded-full mt-2 mr-3 flex-shrink-0"></span>
