              question: "How long does it take to develop a mobile app?",
              answer: "Development time varies from 2-6 months depending on complexity. Simple apps take 2-3 months, while complex applications with advanced features can take 4-6 months. We provide detailed timelines and regular updates throughout the process."
            },
